  <\/div>\r\n                <div class=\"title-insta\">\r\n            <div class=\"st-img-icon\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.atwtravels.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Bank.png\" alt=\"\"><\/div>\r\n            <p class=\"text\">Locating a bank in Singapore is a straightforward task.<\/p>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n                <div class=\"title-insta\">\r\n            <div class=\"st-img-icon\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.atwtravels.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Drinking.png\" alt=\"\"><\/div>\r\n            <p class=\"text\">The legal drinking age in Singapore is 18.<\/p>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n                <div class=\"title-insta\">\r\n            <div class=\"st-img-icon\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.atwtravels.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Prices.png\" alt=\"\"><\/div>\r\n            <p class=\"text\">Prices are typically cheaper in January to May.<\/p>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n                <div class=\"title-insta\">\r\n            <div class=\"st-img-icon\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.atwtravels.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Safest.png\" alt=\"\"><\/div>\r\n            <p class=\"text\">Singaporeans exhibit friendliness and renowned for their hospitality.<\/p>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n        [\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row el_class=&#8221;float-left&#8221; el_id=&#8221;gt_country_tour_details&#8221;][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Singapore &#8211; Visitors Statistics&#8221; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221;][vc_row_inner css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1683352016764{padding-top: 40px !important;}&#8221;][vc_column_inner el_class=&#8221;border-design-right gt-horizontal-map gt-statistics&#8221; width=&#8221;1\/4&#8243;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;30317&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221;][\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=&#8221;border-design-right gt-statistics&#8221; width=&#8221;1\/4&#8243;][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Annually&#8221; font_container=&#8221;tag:h3|text_align:left&#8221; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; el_class=&#8221;gt_statistics_heading_sub&#8221;][vc_column_text el_class=&#8221;tour_gt_number&#8221;]<span class=\"no_desig_gth\">30,00,000<\/span>[\/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class=&#8221;count_no_tour_people&#8221;]<\/p>\n<div class=\"list_gt_div\">\n<div class=\"gt_tour_male\">\n<p class=\"gth_tourm_head\"><span class=\"gth_count_he\">Male<\/span><span class=\"gth_countper\">51%<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"gt_tour_fem\">\n<p class=\"gth_tourm_head\"><span class=\"gth_count_he\">Female<\/span><span class=\"gth_countper\">49%<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=&#8221;border-design-right gt-statistics&#8221; width=&#8221;1\/4&#8243;][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;By Purpose&#8221; font_container=&#8221;tag:h3|text_align:left&#8221; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; el_class=&#8221;gt_statistics_heading_sub&#8221;][vc_column_text el_class=&#8221;purpose_div&#8221;]<\/p>\n<div class=\"gthpurpose\">\n<div class=\"gthpurpose-img\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/gt-hoildays-couple-icon.png\" alt=\"tour package tourism\" \/><\/div>\n<div class=\"gthpurpose-block\">\n<p class=\"gthpurpose-title\">Couples<\/p>\n<p class=\"gthpurpose-text\">For Newlywed Vacations<\/p>\n<div class=\"progress\">\n<div class=\"progress-bar\" style=\"width: 55%;\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class=&#8221;purpose_div&#8221;]<\/p>\n<div class=\"gthpurpose\">\n<div class=\"gthpurpose-img\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/gt-hoildays-family-icon.png\" alt=\"tour packages business\" \/><\/div>\n<div class=\"gthpurpose-block\">\n<p class=\"gthpurpose-title\">Family<\/p>\n<p class=\"gthpurpose-text\">For Family Vacations<\/p>\n<div class=\"progress\">\n<div class=\"progress-bar\" style=\"width: 35%;\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=&#8221;gt-statistics&#8221; width=&#8221;1\/4&#8243;][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Top Visitors from India&#8221; font_container=&#8221;tag:h3|text_align:left&#8221; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; el_class=&#8221;gt_statistics_heading_sub&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<div class=\"gt-top-city\">\n<p class=\"gt-top-city-list\">Bengaluru<\/p>\n<p class=\"gt-top-city-list\">Mumbai<\/p>\n<p class=\"gt-top-city-list\">India<\/p>\n<p class=\"gt-top-city-list\">Delhi<\/p>\n<p class=\"gt-top-city-list\">Hyderabad<\/p>\n<p class=\"gt-top-city-list\">Pune<\/p>\n<p class=\"gt-top-city-list\">Kolkata<\/p>\n<p class=\"gt-top-city-list\">Ahmedabad<\/p>\n<p class=\"gt-top-city-list\">Jaipur<\/p>\n<p class=\"gt-top-city-list\">Lucknow<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1705423622971{margin-top: 20px !important;}&#8221; el_class=&#8221;float-left mob-m0&#8243; el_id=&#8221;package_div_section&#8221;][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;All You Need to Know About Singapore Tour&#8221; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221;][vc_column_text]Can you think of a travel destination that offers you the perfect mixture of nature and technology? Perhaps the kind of place that has both lush greenery as well as modern malls? Well, Singapore is exactly such a destination; a country that has been presenting itself as a delightful amalgamation of almost everything a traveler looks for during their vacation.<\/p>\n<p>From delicious food and high-end restaurants to cultural diversity and architectural marvels, there is a whole world to explore in the country of Singapore, which is something you can do to your heart\u2019s content through our Singapore tour packages. Be it a family-friendly holiday or a trip filled with adventures, our packages have something for everyone. Get ready to relish some scrumptious street food, satisfy your shopaholic self at the local markets, and be awed by the stunning natural landscapes of this island country. [\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column][vc_btn title=&#8221;Read More&#8221; align=&#8221;center&#8221; el_class=&#8221;readmoreBtn&#8221;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row el_id=&#8221;readmoreLayer&#8221;][vc_column][vc_row_inner el_class=&#8221;hide_readless&#8221;][vc_column_inner][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Table of Content:&#8221; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"#about\">About Singapore<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#best-budget-packages\">Best Budget Singapore Tour Packages<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#essential-tips\">Essential Tips To Know Before Travelling To Singapore<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#at-glance\">Singapore At A Glance<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#top-reasons\">Top Reasons To Visit Singapore<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#best-time-to-visit\">Best Time To Visit Singapore<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#things-to-do\">Top Things To Do In Singapore<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#shopping\">Shopping In Singapore<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#things-to-remember\">Things To Remember When Shopping In Singapore<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#foods-to-try-out\">Foods To Try Out In Singapore<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"#art-culture\">Art And Culture In Singapore<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;About Singapore&#8221; font_container=&#8221;tag:h3|text_align:left&#8221; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; el_id=&#8221;about&#8221;][vc_column_text]The island of Singapore was originally inhabited by pirates and fishermen. The Japanese Empire invaded and occupied Singapore during the Second World War from 1942 to 1945. Once the Japanese forces surrendered, British control was established yet again, which led to the merger between Singapore and the Federation of Malaya, thereby causing Malaysia to form in 1963.<\/p>\n<p>Singapore, however, was expelled from Malaysia due to the racial tensions, social unrest, and political problems that took place between Malaysia&#8217;s Alliance Party and the People&#8217;s Action Party (PAP) of Singapore. Hence, it led to the creation of Singapore as an independent republic in August of 1965.[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner el_class=&#8221;hide_readless&#8221;][vc_column_inner][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Tidbits For Infographics&#8221; font_container=&#8221;tag:h3|text_align:left&#8221; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Currency &#8211; Singapore Dollar<\/li>\n<li>Capital City &#8211; Singapore<\/li>\n<li>National Animal &#8211; Asiatic Lion<\/li>\n<li>Languages &#8211; English, Mandarin, Tamil, Malay<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Our Best Budget Singapore Tour Packages&#8221; font_container=&#8221;tag:h3|text_align:left&#8221; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; el_id=&#8221;best-budget-packages&#8221;][vc_column_text el_class=&#8221;tour_table&#8221;]<\/p>\n<table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; border-style: solid; border-color: #000000;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"thead\">\n<td>Singapore Tour Packages<\/td>\n<td>Duration<\/td>\n<td>Highlights<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/www.atwtravels.com\/package\/universal-studios-singapore-tour-package\/\">Amazing Singapore Tour<\/a><\/td>\n<td>3 Nights &amp; 4 Days<\/td>\n<td>Interaction with dolphins, cable car ride, riding the world\u2019s tallest dueling rollercoaster<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/www.atwtravels.com\/package\/exciting-singapore\/\">Exciting Singapore<\/a><\/td>\n<td>4 Nights &amp; 5 Days<\/td>\n<td>Interaction with dolphins, cable car ride, nature park visit<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/www.atwtravels.com\/package\/historic-singapore\/\">Historic Singapore<\/a><\/td>\n<td>3 Nights &amp; 4 Days<\/td>\n<td>Zoo visit, cable car ride, dolphin watching<\/td>\n<\/tr>